I"Ç<h3 class="lead my-5" id="el-operador-ternario-es-un-operador-condicional">El operador ternario es un operador condicional</h3>

<p>Opeador ternario en Python</p>

<div class="language-py highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">language</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'python'</span>

<span class="n">language_check</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">True</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">language</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s">'python'</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="bp">False</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">language_check</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1">#Output: True
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="operador-ternario-en-javascript">Operador ternario en JavaScript</h2>

<p>El operador ternario en javascript toma tres par√°metros: una condici√≥n seguida del signo interrogante  <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">?</code>, una expresi√≥n que se ejecutar√° si la condici√≥n es verdadera y seguido por dos puntos <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">:</code> la expresi√≥n que se ejecutar√° si la condici√≥n es falsa.</p>

<div class="language-js highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">language</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">javascript</span><span class="dl">'</span>

<span class="kd">var</span> <span class="nx">check_language</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">language</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="dl">'</span><span class="s1">javascript</span><span class="dl">'</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="p">?</span> <span class="kc">true</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="kc">false</span><span class="p">;</span>

<span class="nx">console</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">log</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">check_language</span><span class="p">);</span>

<span class="c1">// Output: true</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
